telegram-plugin-rs
==================

This crate is a Rust port of the official Telegram channel plugin for
Claude Code, originally authored by Anthropic in TypeScript:

    https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official
    Path:    external_plugins/telegram
    Source commit: 3449c10cd1f254c2529a4a7e96a094ef118a00a5

Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. See LICENSE for the full
license text. You may obtain a copy of the License at:

    http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Modifications relative to the upstream TypeScript implementation:

  - Reimplemented in Rust against tokio + frankenstein (replaces bun +
    grammy + @modelcontextprotocol/sdk).
  - Optional voice transcription via whisper-cli subprocess, backported
    from codefather-labs/claude-plugins-official.

